# custom.txt.example — copy this file to custom.txt to get started:
#   cp allowlist-domains.d/custom.txt.example allowlist-domains.d/custom.txt
#
# custom.txt is gitignored so your internal hostnames stay out of version control.
# It is always included regardless of which components are enabled.
# Add any additional domains here: internal registries, MCP server endpoints,
# search engines, or anything else your AI agents need to reach at runtime.
#
# Examples:
#   google.com
#   your-internal-registry.example.com
#   your-mcp-server.example.com
